# Spec: {{PROJECT_NAME}} Frontend

Domain: {{DOMAIN}}

This frontend pack defines the operator and driver-facing UI workflows for parking management. It is designed to be expanded into a frontend SDD project and implemented from the generated traceability, use cases, command/query contracts, and Gherkin scenarios.

Primary user outcomes:
- Operators can monitor capacity and detect operational exceptions.
- Gate staff or automated kiosks can register vehicle entry when capacity allows.
- Drivers or attendants can review calculated fees before payment.
- Operators can review overstays for enforcement.
- Drivers can see receipt delivery status after successful payment.
